&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "44",
&"next_id": "45",
&"text": "Her eyes and hair really stand out, don't they?",
&"type": "dialogue"
},
"45": {
&"character": "Caleb",
&"id": "45",
&"next_id": "46",
&"text": "So she hides between classes in the club room, Naomi's special guest",
