raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do unlock_gallery_image(\"caleb\", \"1\")
Caleb: Hey friend! 👋
Caleb: Thanks for coming this afternoon
Player: Caleb?
Caleb: Yeah!
Player: Thanks for inviting me
Caleb: It was awesome to have you!
Caleb: I hope you don't mind that Naomi gave me your number
Player: No problem!
Caleb: Actually she was supposed to text you but she got caught up with work 😅
if Story.red_heart >= 1:
	Caleb: She said a lot of nice things about you the other day!
	Player: Really?
	Caleb: Yup!
Caleb: You might hear from her soon
Caleb: But anyway!
Caleb: I also wanted to send you the pictures we took today!
Player: That sounds good
Caleb: I had to use an old film that had a bit of space left on it
Caleb: A lot of them came out nice so I'll forward what I have 😊
Player: Awesome, lets see
Caleb: img: mabel/56
Player: They had a really good time
Caleb: I'm glad Mabel and Naomi are clicking well together
Caleb: I feel like it's been a while since the clubhouse was this lively
Caleb: It's usually a lot more quiet
Player: Why's that?
Caleb: Just not as many members as before
Caleb: There's been a bit of gossip about us and we've had trouble getting new members since then 😓
Caleb: Anyway, I don't want to be a downer!
Caleb: Especially after the two had a really good time!
if Story.mabel_trust >= 60:
	Caleb: img: alice/1
	Caleb: Alice actually sat down with us for a bit today 🙂
	Caleb: Naomi begged her to meet Mabel
	Caleb: She had a good feeling about them becoming friends I guess!
	Player: She didn't say much
	Caleb: Yeah.. Alice is not much of a talker
	Player: Is she part of your photography club?
	Caleb: Not exactly...
	Caleb: She's had a pretty bad college experience so far 😞
	Caleb: Sorority girls really pick on her hard because of her appearance
	Caleb: Her eyes and hair really stand out, don't they?
	Caleb: So she hides between classes in the club room, Naomi's special guest
	Caleb: Poor girl 😕
	- She doesn't look weird to me
		set Story.flag = \"AliceNotWeird\"
		Player: She doesn't look weird to me
		Caleb: Really? Have you met girls that look like her before?
		Player: Not really
		Caleb: Oh, well it's just something that's different I guess
		Caleb: Maybe talk to her when you get the chance, I'm sure she'd be happy to hear that
		Caleb: But she's usually quite shy and skittish haha so good luck!
	- [Say Nothing]
Caleb: Here's the next one
Caleb: delete: img: valerie/7
Caleb: Oh crap
Caleb: Uhm, wait a sec
Caleb: Sorry...
Caleb: Just ignore what you saw 😅 Must've been on the old film
- She looks a bit familiar [if Story.brown_heart >= 1]
	set Story.flag = \"CalebActingStrange\"
	Player: She looks a bit familiar..
	Caleb: Ah don't worry about it
	Caleb: It's nothing at all
	Caleb: Just some old memories
- [Don't ask]
Caleb: Here's the one I meant to send
Caleb: img: caleb/2
Caleb: This turned out to be a good picture of us haha
Player: Except I'm barely in it lol
if Story.mabel_desire > 10:
	Caleb: img: mabel/57
	Caleb: Oh and then the AC went down again lol 😰
	Caleb: Sorry about that haha
	Caleb: Naomi's totally gonna be mad at the company 😝
	Player: That's okay, we got this picture out of it 😁
	Caleb: True!
	Caleb: Oh uhm, I mean of Naomi... 😅
	Caleb: Anywayy
Caleb: Well that was all that was in my reel
Caleb: It's a bummer that Ms Suzanna wasn't able to join us today
Player: Mabel's professor?
Caleb: Yep!
Caleb: I think she had a date 😅
- Date? She's not married?
	Player: Date? She's not married?
	Caleb: Well, no
	Caleb: She's having trouble with that 😅
	Caleb: They all seem to be interested in younger women but don't tell her I told you 😓
	Caleb: She's only 31 though!
	Caleb: The ones that do go out with her end up trying to get her into one night stands 🙂
	Caleb: And she's not really into that
	Player: That's sad...
	Player: How do you know all this?
	Caleb: Well... In our club, we've got a pretty strong trust circle and she's a part of it
	Caleb: We tell each other everything and support each other where we can 😇
	- I wonder if she'd be interested in dating a student [#orangeheart]
		set Story.orange_heart += 1
		Player: I wonder if she'd be interested in dating a student
		Caleb: Oh, I have no idea
		Caleb: I don't know how I'd ask her about that so maybe you could ask her yourself
		Caleb: I just always assumed not
	- That's really cool
		Player: That's really cool
		Caleb: You think so?
		Caleb: A lot of other groups think we're a super lame club
		Caleb: I'm glad you think otherwise!
- Is she a part of the club?
	Player: Is she a part of the club?
	Caleb: Well sort of
	Caleb: Clubs are usually funded by a faculty member so she backs us
	Caleb: She's really kind to us, hopefully you'll meet her next time
Player: Thanks for sharing!
Caleb: Was there anything else?
- Do you have a Social acc I could follow?
	Player: Do you have a Social acc I could follow?
	Caleb: Sure!
	set PhoneUnlocks.reveal = \"caleb\"
- That's all!
	Player: That's all!
Caleb: I hope you'll visit us more often!
Caleb: Naomi says hi and to tell you that the both of you are welcome any time!
Player: Thanks, might do when we can
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
